{"tid":837402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轟炸阿富汗！美將首度讓F-35投入實戰","createTime":"2018-09-26T10:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T01:39:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"83c2c1dbefb879b5a79236965588e382c67bc57c","tid":837402,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-09-26/656/20180926001275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-09-26%2F656%2F20180926001275.jpg&h=321865ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一架F-35B戰機9月16日準備從在亞丁灣的「埃塞克斯」號兩棲攻擊艦起飛。（美國海軍）<br />\n<br />\n近日內美國海軍陸戰隊的F-35B隱形戰機可能出動，首度執行戰鬥任務。據數名五角大廈官員說，這些5代戰機正在美國海軍黃蜂級（Wasp-class）「埃塞克斯」號（USS Essex，LHD 2）兩棲攻擊艦上，應該很快就會在阿富汗針對暴亂份子執行轟炸任務。<br />\n<br />\n據CNN新聞網與《商業內幕》（Business Insider）網25日報導，一名官員透露，「埃塞克斯」號已從亞丁灣出發，進入北阿拉伯海（North Arabian Sea），預料即將駛入波斯灣。而F-35駕駛在待命的同時，一直在索馬利亞執行情報蒐集與偵察任務，但至今尚未參與過戰鬥。<br />\n<br />\n儘管美國空軍率先宣佈，F-35A已經能備戰，但看來海軍陸戰隊可能會成為第一個讓F-35投入戰鬥的美國軍種。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍陸戰隊的F-35B能短場/垂直起降，讓它得以在比航母小得多的兩棲攻擊艦上執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n不過，率先讓F-35執行戰鬥任務的世界紀錄，已在5月由以色列創下。據CNN與《防務新聞》（Defense News）報導，以色列5月下旬時推文宣佈，F-35I「全能王」（Adir）已在敘利亞執行戰鬥任務。<br />\n<br />\n而以色列媒體也引述該國空軍指揮官諾金（Amikam Norkin）的話說，以色列F-35戰機的飛行範圍已涵蓋全中東，並已在兩個不同的戰線發動兩次攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n此外，據《耶路撒冷郵報》（The Jerusalem Post）報導，諾金在發表談話時，就站在一張以色列F-35戰機飛越黎巴嫩首都貝魯特的照片前。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180926001207-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180926001207-260417&d=Df%2F4XjLza5srvzb%2B%2BQj%2Fb0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5ad63fac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180926001207-260417</a>"},{"pid":"ad5c3ec30ef8709ce1da830668862d7d31cbe9a3","tid":837402,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n練兵"},{"pid":"fd538e177d8eabc1ce81cf47b77de83f5492f21e","tid":837402,"uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"F-35I「全能王」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbf7a6194608a49c5ad9768ac8d386427d43ced","tid":837402,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"猶太人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddcabeb9dab3f381b56089b69f3d5460cc4aead","tid":837402,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"猶太人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170fc53cd6f98b9a422c2329dc85cb2bb1e67ab8","tid":837402,"uid":33456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"全能到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41208c85305cb250d507787733bfef13655bf46","tid":837402,"uid":94739,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"美帝打哂真軍咁練兵<br />\n<br />\n解放軍依然仲摺緊被<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50ec36d88f924501ba5057fd2c02e81822aab3f","tid":837402,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a41208c85305cb250d507787733bfef13655bf46","tid":837402,"uid":94739,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"美帝打哂真軍咁練兵<br />\n<br />\n解放軍依然仲摺緊被<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"前年賣咗幾件去印尼軍演唔係已經炸鳩咗幾個大魚? <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1503e